data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME WITH AWESOME BUILTINS WON'T LAST LONG. MANY UPDATES OVER THE PAST COUPLE OF YEARS INCLUDE, CARPET, PAINT, SOME UPDATED PLUMBING AND WIRING, ROOF AND THE LAUNDRY ROOM MOVED TO THE BASEMENT ADDING AN ADDITIONAL BEDROOM ON MAIN LEVEL. THE OVERSIZED 2 CAR GARAGE IS HEATED AND HAS ADDITIONAL ATTIC STORAGE. THE WHOLE HOUSE FAN WILL HELP KEEP YOU COOL THIS SUMMER. LARGE BACK YARD WITH DECK IS PERFECT FOR YOUR SUMMER ACTIVITIES. TAKE A LOOK TODAY AND MAKE THIS HOUSE YOUR HOME!
